# Paper AI Project Rules

1. Better Auth library for authentication
2. All new features must have real-time sync consideration
3. Editor implementation uses BlockNote with PartyKit
4. UI follows Shadcn component patterns
5. Protected routes use middleware auth checks
6. Postgres/Prisma for all data persistence
7. Zustand for client-state management
8. React Query for server state and data fetching
9. TypeScript strict mode enabled
10. Components follow atomic design
11. Real-time features use PartyKit for collaboration
